dsense.name: interleave [sth] with [sth]
dsense.guideword: often passive (insert [sth] between pages of a book)

example.eg: The bookbinder interleaved the sketchbook with glassine.
example.egtrans: 装订工在速写本页间夹上了蜡光纸。

example.eg: The pages of the medieval text had been interleaved with archival paper to protect the images.
